name: Colors in Space(Trapped)
description:
It's getting faster, moving faster now, getting out of control, I've got the spirit, and sometimes losing the feeling, somehow letting go. But we are all still here, stuck with the same Space and Reality, TRAPPED. But my bubbles still slows down, as it should. this is our journey to see the Absurdity of life and guessing every Confusion.

Series : "(Your) Confusion & Bubbles"
